809
01:13:46,668 --> 01:13:50,096
So why put up with it?
A few pills, that's all it would take.

810
01:13:50,106 --> 01:13:53,429
But I am happy.

811
01:13:53,442 --> 01:13:56,766
I have a friend here with me.

812
01:14:00,148 --> 01:14:02,003
GIRL:
Hello?

813
01:14:03,517 --> 01:14:04,702
