826
01:14:47,929 --> 01:14:52,287
Surely you remember.
We're frying chicken.

827
01:14:52,298 --> 01:14:55,918
But we have to be careful, don't we,
because oil is hot.

828
01:14:55,935 --> 01:14:58,623
Oil gets very hot.

829
01:14:58,639 --> 01:15:03,998
